title: I would recommend !
text: I love this app! You can buy so many things and get coupons! I would recommend this app if your starting to buy stuff!😁

I was a bit skeptical about ordering from shein at first, but then my order came and I was impressed. Its been a year and a half now and I've order clothes and some hair stuff and I've only had an issue once. It wasn't even their fault there was just a delay due to weather. I'm so glad I tried it because I could never afford clothes that I actually liked! I recommend this to anyone who is struggling to afford things because this is so affordable and good quality!

title: Read this if you want the truth about Shein ✨
text: To start very affordable very very cute and did I mention affordable because how many times can I say this this app is probably one of the most affordable things you can invest in in your life. this app has a variety and things but I would not recommend the skin care or any facial cares because sometimes it can be a little bit cheap,but the clothes, and  cute things you wanna buy for your kids or even yourself buy it.The only unfortunate thing about this is that these things are coming from a very far distance away if you live in the United States so the estimate of how much time your orders would get here is probably at most 2 to 3 weeks. another unfortunate thing about this app is that sometimes it can be a little bit deceiving with pictures or the front cover because sometimes they’re not always the quality that they present, which is kind of a downer. other than that and amazing download it on your phone or any device right now.
